OL,3,C'Killer' refused treatment for 70%
OL,4,Cburns after deadly fire, trial told
OL,6,FAn alleged killer refused treatment
OL,7,Ffor 70% burns after starting the house
OL,8,Ffire which left a mother and three
OL,9,Fchildren dead, his murder trial has
OL,10,Fheard.
OL,12,FProsecutors say Sharaz Ali set fire to
OL,13,Fthe Bradford home of Bryonie Gawith
OL,14,Fand her children in a failed revenge
OL,15,Fattack on his former partner `
OL,16,FBryonie's sister, Antonia Gawith.
