OL,3,C'Killer' refused treatment for 70%
OL,4,Cburns after deadly fire, trial told
OL,6,FJurors have heard that Ali was pulled
OL,7,Ffrom the fire on Westbury Road by
OL,8,Fpolice officers who arrived at the
OL,9,Fscene first and managed to break the
OL,10,Fback door down.
OL,12,FBut Bryonie, 29, and her three
OL,13,Fchildren - nine-year-old Denisty
OL,14,FBirtle, Oscar Birtle, five, and 22-
OL,15,Fmonth-old Aubree Birtle - were trapped
OL,16,Fupstairs. They died at the scene.
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, Doncaster Crown Court
OL,19,Fheard that Ali refused treatment from
OL,20,Fparamedics following the fire in the
OL,21,Fearly hours of 21 August last year.
