OL,3,C'Killer' refused treatment for 70%
OL,4,Cburns after deadly fire, trial told
OL,6,FA statement from PC Wilson, who
OL,7,Fattended, said Ali was rejecting
OL,8,Foxygen and fluids and put his head in
OL,9,Fhis hands when he was arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of murder and attempted
OL,11,Fmurder.
OL,13,FHe said medical teams eventually
OL,14,Fmanaged to calm Ali down and give him
OL,15,Foxygen before he was taken to hospital.
OL,17,FThe court heard he continued to refuse
OL,18,Ftreatment and wouldn't allow anyone to
OL,19,Ftouch him, but a doctor "made the
OL,20,Fdecision to override this and gave him
OL,21,Fsome drugs to knock him unconscious".
