OL,4,Cburns after deadly fire, trial told
OL,6,FA statement from another officer, Pc
OL,7,FShauna McKee, said when she attended
OL,8,FLeeds General Infirmary, Ali was
OL,9,Fseverely injured and his care team
OL,10,Fsaid he was in a critical condition,
OL,11,Fwith burns to 70% of his body.
OL,13,FJurors have heard Ali was placed into
OL,14,Fan induced coma for months before his
OL,15,Frecovery began.
