OL,3,C'Killer' refused treatment for 70%
OL,4,Cburns after deadly fire, trial told
OL,6,FProsecutors say Ali was "motivated by
OL,7,Fjealousy and fuelled by drink and
OL,8,Fdrugs" when he went to Bryonie's house
OL,9,Fon Westbury Road, Bradford, where
OL,10,FAntonia Gawith was staying after
OL,11,Fending their "abusive" seven-year
OL,12,Frelationship, earlier that month.
OL,14,FLast week, Antonia Gawith told the
OL,15,Ftrial she came downstairs after
OL,16,Fhearing a noise and saw Ali force his
OL,17,Fway into the house with another man
OL,18,Fand then pour petrol around the house,
OL,19,Fon her and on himself.
