OL,6,FShe said she ran outside thinking he
OL,7,Fwould follow her, but when he did not,
OL,8,Fshe went back and saw Ali climbing the
OL,9,Fstairs. He was kicked down by Bryonie,
OL,10,Fwho had woken up.
OL,12,FAntonia Gawith said she saw Ali use a
OL,13,Flighter to start the fire, before the
OL,14,Ffront door swung shut, and said when
OL,15,Fshe managed to open it, there was
OL,16,F"fire everywhere".
