OL,6,FShe described trying to open the back
OL,7,Fdoor, which was jammed, while shouting
OL,8,Ffor help for her sister, nieces and
OL,9,Fnephew, who were trapped inside as
OL,10,Fflames engulfed the house.
OL,12,FAli, 40, of no fixed address, and
OL,13,FCalum Sunderland, 26, of Calton
OL,14,FStreet, Keighley, are charged with
OL,15,Fmurdering Bryonie and the three
OL,16,Fchildren and attempting to murder
OL,17,FAntonia.
