OL,6,FMohammed Shabir, 45, who had been due
OL,7,Fto go on trial with them, died of a
OL,8,Fheart attack last month after
OL,9,Fcollapsing in prison.
OL,11,FProsecutors say Shabir drove to and
OL,12,Ffrom the house while Sunderland kicked
OL,13,Fthe door in.
OL,15,FAli and Sunderland deny the charges
OL,16,Fand the trial continues.
